---
title: Sweet & Sticky Asian Chicken with Coconut Rice & Garlic Veggie Stir-Fry
description: There’s something seriously addictive about succulent chicken strips coated in this sweet and sticky sauce, which has a touch of zing from the addition of ginger. Just add fragrant coconut rice and tender veg for a meal that's sure to be a new favourite.
